00:24:27,710 --> 00:24:28,540
Turn on the power and try it.

297
00:24:28,960 --> 00:24:29,810
If it works,

298
00:24:29,880 --> 00:24:31,130
we'll take blood clots

299
00:24:31,130 --> 00:24:32,170
for all limb necrosis patients.

300
00:24:34,600 --> 00:24:35,220
Are you sure

301
00:24:35,440 --> 00:24:36,260
you want to do an intervention
in a place like this

302
00:24:36,270 --> 00:24:37,610
with a gastrointestinal machine?

303
00:24:38,360 --> 00:24:39,130
Yes.

304
00:24:40,120 --> 00:24:41,400
