305
00:24:41,400 --> 00:24:43,540
Prepare the power supply now.

306
00:24:44,160 --> 00:24:45,060
There aren't that many aftershocks.

307
00:24:48,960 --> 00:24:50,130
Why don't you persuade him?

308
00:24:51,070 --> 00:24:51,960
I haven't made it

309
00:24:51,960 --> 00:24:52,980
since the day I met him.

310
00:24:53,230 --> 00:24:54,220
Why don't you try?

311
00:24:59,310 --> 00:24:59,980
Carry it over here.

312
00:25:00,600 --> 00:25:01,260
Move the water there.

313
00:25:01,260 --> 00:25:01,920
[Disaster relief]

314
00:25:01,920 --> 00:25:02,550
Be quick.

315
00:25:02,550 --> 00:25:03,330
Commander Zhao!

316
00:25:04,640 --> 00:25:05,370
Commander Zhao!

317
00:25:06,640 --> 00:25:07,610
What else do you want?

318
00:25:07,750 --> 00:25:08,510
A generator.

319
00:25:08,510 --> 00:25:09,460
There's only one.

320
00:25:09,680 --> 00:25:10,610
Director Kong is using it.

321
00:25:10,750 --> 00:25:11,650
He needs to power the ventilator

322
00:25:11,650 --> 00:25:12,370
for the operation.

323
00:25:12,440 --> 00:25:13,700
Please contact headquarters for me.

324
00:25:13,920 --> 00:25:15,300
Tell the rescue helicopter

325
00:25:15,440 --> 00:25:16,410
to bring me lead aprons,

326
00:25:16,440 --> 00:25:17,880
regular catheters,
embolization catheters,

327
00:25:17,880 --> 00:25:18,980
contrast agents, embolic agents,

328
00:25:18,990 --> 00:25:19,780
plus,

329
00:25:20,070 --> 00:25:21,410
a diesel generator.

330
00:25:21,710 --> 00:25:22,840
If we get him all this stuff,

331
00:25:22,840 --> 00:25:23,980
he can save at least ten more people.

332
00:25:24,070 --> 00:25:24,810
Twenty.

333
00:25:25,230 --> 00:25:25,980
Per day.

334
00:25:26,200 --> 00:25:27,270
Ask them to mobilize nephrologists

335
00:25:27,270 --> 00:25:28,310
and dialysis machines

336
00:25:28,310 --> 00:25:29,330
from all over the country.

337
00:25:29,510 --> 00:25:31,020
This is very important.

338
00:25:31,030 --> 00:25:32,170
Please make it happen.

339
00:25:32,270 --> 00:25:33,020
Isn't emergency care

340
00:25:33,070 --> 00:25:34,330
mainly surgical?

341
00:25:34,360 --> 00:25:35,540
Why do we need so many nephrologists?

342
00:25:35,540 --> 00:25:35,960
What's the point?

343
00:25:35,960 --> 00:25:36,980
There will be a large number

344
00:25:36,980 --> 00:25:37,920
of patients with acute kidney failure

345
00:25:37,920 --> 00:25:39,500
in the next few days.

346
00:25:39,600 --> 00:25:40,840
The number will be staggering.

347
00:25:40,840 --> 00:25:41,890
We need to prepare in advance.

348
00:25:42,840 --> 00:25:44,230
Okay, I'll get right on it.

349
00:25:44,230 --> 00:25:44,940
OK.

350
00:25:45,270 --> 00:25:45,940
Thank you.

351
00:25:48,400 --> 00:25:49,330
Where's He?

352
00:25:49,710 --> 00:25:50,460
Where did he go?

353
00:25:56,990 --> 00:25:58,170
Eating noodles, Boy?

354
00:25:59,510 --> 00:26:00,130
Boy.

355
00:26:00,510 --> 00:26:02,260
Do you usually read fantasy?

356
00:26:03,030 --> 00:26:05,130
Sun Wukong once said

357
00:26:05,510 --> 00:26:06,570
suffering

358
00:26:06,680 --> 00:26:08,330
is a training for people.

359
00:26:08,640 --> 00:26:09,090
Sickness...

360
00:26:09,840 --> 00:26:10,710
Pigsy, let's go.

361
00:26:10,710 --> 00:26:11,740
To the West to fetch scriptures.

362
00:26:11,750 --> 00:26:13,470
Don't think about going back
to the Gaolaozhuang.

363
00:26:13,470 --> 00:26:14,810
I'll go with you,

364
00:26:14,840 --> 00:26:15,810
but it hurts too much.

365
00:26:16,070 --> 00:26:17,130
What are you doing? Chatting?

366
00:26:17,200 --> 00:26:18,410
I'm doing counseling.

367
00:26:18,470 --> 00:26:20,780
Do you know how important counseling is?

368
00:26:20,840 --> 00:26:21,680
Pigsy.

369
00:26:21,680 --> 00:26:23,060
You're an anesthesiologist.

370
00:26:23,160 --> 00:26:24,600
Do you have a counselor license?

371
00:26:24,600 --> 00:26:25,540
- Come back with me.
- Wait.

372
00:26:25,600 --> 00:26:26,880
I'm a shining light.

373
00:26:26,880 --> 00:26:27,700
You think you're the sun?

374
00:26:27,700 --> 00:26:28,700
Shining light?

375
00:26:40,200 --> 00:26:41,540
It's moving! Now.

376
00:26:43,760 --> 00:26:44,650
Be careful.

377
00:26:45,550 --> 00:26:46,260
Be careful.

378
00:26:46,400 --> 00:26:46,790
Be careful.

379
00:26:46,790 --> 00:26:48,330
Watch your step!

380
00:26:58,230 --> 00:26:59,410
Watch your step!

381
00:26:59,900 --> 00:27:01,130
Take it easy!

382
00:27:03,160 --> 00:27:04,850
Move the goods over here.

383
00:27:10,790 --> 00:27:12,220
Major Gao, thank you.

384
00:27:12,270 --> 00:27:13,120
The nearest unit

385
00:27:13,120 --> 00:27:13,980
is only 20 kilometers away.

386
00:27:14,200 --> 00:27:15,220
They'll be here soon.

387
00:27:15,470 --> 00:27:16,090
That's great.

388
00:27:16,590 --> 00:27:17,840
My previous suggestion?

389
00:27:17,990 --> 00:27:19,330
The wounded have been sent
to Hexi Province.

390
00:27:19,710 --> 00:27:20,830
And I've reported the contents

391
00:27:20,920 --> 00:27:21,890
in the notebook.

392
00:27:22,030 --> 00:27:23,060
The leaders are taking it seriously.

393
00:27:23,510 --> 00:27:24,940
Orders have been given to the front.

394
00:27:24,990 --> 00:27:26,360
In a few days,

395
00:27:26,360 --> 00:27:27,930
more than 1,000 nephrologists
will arrive.

396
00:27:28,680 --> 00:27:29,540
The generator?

397
00:27:29,920 --> 00:27:30,880
Did you bring the generator?

398
00:27:30,880 --> 00:27:31,540
Yes.

399
00:27:31,710 --> 00:27:32,570
That's great.

400
00:27:33,360 --> 00:27:34,740
We're finally ready for surgery.

401
00:27:36,400 --> 00:27:37,310
We haven't eaten, drunk, or slept

402
00:27:37,310 --> 00:27:38,980
for over 30 hours.

403
00:27:39,030 --> 00:27:39,780
Pigsy.

404
00:27:39,780 --> 00:27:41,460
Don't you want to shine?

405
00:27:41,460 --> 00:27:42,470
Let's go. Get the generator.

406
00:27:42,470 --> 00:27:43,960
Even the sun goes down sometimes.

407
00:27:43,960 --> 00:27:45,610
Then I'll go on with my mission.

408
00:27:46,440 --> 00:27:47,020
Major Gao.

409
00:27:48,600 --> 00:27:49,090
Here.

410
00:27:50,460 --> 00:27:51,740
[Interventional consumables list]

411
00:27:52,270 --> 00:27:52,890
Consumables.

412
00:27:53,470 --> 00:27:54,220
Please bring more

413
00:27:54,510 --> 00:27:55,700
interventional consumables next time.

414
00:27:55,880 --> 00:27:56,570
Thank you, sir.

415
00:27:56,990 --> 00:27:57,740
Don't worry.

416
00:28:07,230 --> 00:28:08,130
Can it work?

417
00:28:09,840 --> 00:28:10,700
No problem.

418
00:28:14,440 --> 00:28:16,460
Okay, that's it.

419
00:28:16,650 --> 00:28:17,790
Just see.

420
00:28:20,070 --> 00:28:20,810
Here you go.

421
00:28:23,120 --> 00:28:24,060
It's on.

422
00:28:32,840 --> 00:28:34,130
How did I do?

423
00:28:34,230 --> 00:28:35,260
I thought

424
00:28:35,440 --> 00:28:36,220
I'd become an electrician

425
00:28:36,400 --> 00:28:37,220
if I didn't become a doctor.

426
00:28:37,360 --> 00:28:38,220
The electrician is better for you.

427
00:28:38,790 --> 00:28:39,540
Really?

428
00:28:43,440 --> 00:28:43,980
Lin Yuan.

429
00:28:46,270 --> 00:28:46,780
Lin Yuan.

430
00:28:47,200 --> 00:28:48,650
How about
the interventional consumables?

431
00:28:50,120 --> 00:28:50,940
We don't have any lead aprons.

432
00:28:53,070 --> 00:28:53,740
What should we do?

433
00:28:54,920 --> 00:28:56,310
We're really going
to be exposed to radiation.

434
00:28:56,310 --> 00:28:57,020
This...

435
00:29:00,550 --> 00:29:01,130
Don't worry.

436
00:29:01,680 --> 00:29:03,020
A gastrointestinal machine's radiation
is low.

437
00:29:03,750 --> 00:29:04,460
You can all leave now.

438
00:29:04,790 --> 00:29:05,640
I can do it myself.

439
00:29:06,360 --> 00:29:07,210
Thank you, Mr. Zheng.

440
00:29:07,210 --> 00:29:08,380
Pigsy, stop right there.

441
00:29:09,310 --> 00:29:09,890
Where are you going?

442
00:29:10,030 --> 00:29:11,370
X-rays.

443
00:29:11,370 --> 00:29:12,160
You have a daughter.

444
00:29:12,160 --> 00:29:13,330
Why are you afraid of this?

445
00:29:14,310 --> 00:29:14,940
Besides,

446
00:29:15,280 --> 00:29:16,980
this building will collapse
in an aftershock

447
00:29:17,030 --> 00:29:17,780
of magnitude six or higher.

448
00:29:17,920 --> 00:29:19,170
I'll support it if it collapses.

449
00:29:19,840 --> 00:29:20,570
OK.

450
00:29:21,440 --> 00:29:22,090
Lin Yuan.

451
00:29:22,510 --> 00:29:23,170
Get out of here.

452
00:29:24,030 --> 00:29:24,850
I'm not afraid of rays.

453
00:29:24,960 --> 00:29:25,980
We don't need so many people here.

454
00:29:26,160 --> 00:29:27,170
There are other patients out there.

455
00:29:27,510 --> 00:29:28,090
But I...

456
00:29:28,090 --> 00:29:28,890
But what?

457
00:29:28,990 --> 00:29:29,650
Go.

458
00:29:30,160 --> 00:29:30,940
Just go.

459
00:29:42,030 --> 00:29:43,300
How is it? Does it work?

460
00:29:45,310 --> 00:29:46,130
It's blurry.

461
00:29:50,030 --> 00:29:50,850
Tell them

462
00:29:51,160 --> 00:29:52,260
to bring Bai Yang's mom here.

463
00:29:55,960 --> 00:29:57,130
Boy, are you okay?

464
00:29:57,790 --> 00:29:58,370
Boy.

465
00:29:58,550 --> 00:29:59,740
Doctor? Is there a doctor?

466
00:29:59,740 --> 00:30:00,330
- I'm here.
- Come on.

467
00:30:00,400 --> 00:30:01,850
What's wrong with him?

468
00:30:03,160 --> 00:30:03,810
What happened to him?

469
00:30:03,920 --> 00:30:05,580
He's suddenly unconscious.

470
00:30:05,580 --> 00:30:07,330
Sir?

471
00:30:18,030 --> 00:30:18,890
Liver rupture.

472
00:30:19,120 --> 00:30:19,890
We need to operate immediately.

473
00:30:20,070 --> 00:30:20,990
Call an anesthesiologist.

474
00:30:21,320 --> 00:30:22,750
There's no anesthesiologist.

475
00:30:23,510 --> 00:30:24,620
You'll have to do it.

476
00:30:26,200 --> 00:30:26,840
His pulse is weak.

477
00:30:27,400 --> 00:30:28,980
His blood pressure is 60 at most.

478
00:30:29,270 --> 00:30:30,090
Adrenaline.

479
00:30:45,550 --> 00:30:46,500
Sufentanil.

480
00:30:49,440 --> 00:30:51,090
Ten micrograms should do it.

481
00:31:02,990 --> 00:31:04,330
Pull his shirt up.

482
00:31:07,440 --> 00:31:09,090
Come on, help me get dressed.

483
00:31:20,470 --> 00:31:21,460
Why isn't it sterilized?

484
00:31:39,270 --> 00:31:40,200
What's going on here, Doc?

485
00:31:40,200 --> 00:31:41,260
Come on, do something!

486
00:31:45,030 --> 00:31:46,330
Do something!

487
00:31:48,600 --> 00:31:50,120
Do something!

488
00:31:51,020 --> 00:31:51,820
What's going on here?

489
00:31:52,510 --> 00:31:53,340
Liver rupture.

490
00:31:55,360 --> 00:31:56,300
It's a neurological reflex

491
00:31:56,360 --> 00:31:57,840
caused by a liver laceration.

492
00:31:58,160 --> 00:31:59,260
We need to block it now.

493
00:31:59,960 --> 00:32:01,050
How much anesthesia did you give him?

494
00:32:01,050 --> 00:32:02,160
Ten micrograms of sufentanil.

495
00:32:02,160 --> 00:32:03,020
That's not enough.

496
00:32:05,230 --> 00:32:06,540
Doctor, hurry up.

497
00:32:28,400 --> 00:32:28,980
Done.

498
00:32:30,360 --> 00:32:31,090
Prepare for surgery.

499
00:32:49,790 --> 00:32:51,300
Don't just stand there. Come and help.

500
00:33:36,580 --> 00:33:38,700
[Nanyang Town Health Center]

501
00:34:01,360 --> 00:34:02,740
Slow down. You're going too fast.

502
00:34:02,790 --> 00:34:03,650
I didn't get a good look.

503
00:34:03,750 --> 00:34:05,330
That's why you're not cut out
for interventions.

504
00:34:05,840 --> 00:34:07,370
Just be a good anesthesiologist.

505
00:34:11,280 --> 00:34:12,340
The guidewire is already

506
00:34:12,340 --> 00:34:13,540
in the anterior tibial artery
of the calf.

507
00:34:14,440 --> 00:34:15,290
Done.

508
00:34:16,920 --> 00:34:18,090
Amazing.

509
00:34:18,440 --> 00:34:19,650
Yun's doing well, too.

510
00:34:19,990 --> 00:34:20,820
Don't talk.

511
00:34:23,070 --> 00:34:23,860
Catheter for thrombus extraction.

512
00:34:31,590 --> 00:34:32,340
Zheng Ren, slow down.

513
00:34:32,440 --> 00:34:33,290
The image is too blurry.

514
00:34:33,290 --> 00:34:33,900
I can't see it clearly.

515
00:34:33,960 --> 00:34:35,040
That's right, Zheng.

516
00:34:35,280 --> 00:34:37,020
This machine is aging too badly.

517
00:34:37,110 --> 00:34:37,820
It's full of artifacts.

518
00:34:38,150 --> 00:34:39,420
How exactly did you determine

519
00:34:39,470 --> 00:34:41,210
where the micro guidewire was?

520
00:34:43,320 --> 00:34:44,060
The contrast agent.

521
00:35:05,240 --> 00:35:06,020
Right here.

522
00:35:12,510 --> 00:35:13,170
Take the thrombus.

523
00:35:22,030 --> 00:35:22,860
The contrast agent.

524
00:35:32,470 --> 00:35:34,060
I'm just getting a general vision.

525
00:35:34,320 --> 00:35:35,610
A general idea
about the micro guidewire's location.

526
00:35:36,550 --> 00:35:37,690
There's no way to do chemoembolization.

527
00:35:37,760 --> 00:35:38,690
How did you do it?

528
00:35:39,320 --> 00:35:40,570
You can do it in the future.

529
00:35:41,720 --> 00:35:42,460
The necrotic surfaces

530
00:35:42,460 --> 00:35:43,170
have already been treated.

531
00:35:43,800 --> 00:35:44,690
Reduced the edema

532
00:35:45,240 --> 00:35:46,110
to speed up

533
00:35:46,110 --> 00:35:47,230
the blood circulation.

534
00:35:47,310 --> 00:35:48,440
It's a good thing

535
00:35:49,150 --> 00:35:51,130
we saved her ankle.

536
00:35:51,960 --> 00:35:52,650
Surgery is complete.

537
00:35:53,590 --> 00:35:54,730
We can notify Commander Zhao

538
00:35:54,840 --> 00:35:56,090
to bring the other patients in.

539
00:35:56,090 --> 00:35:57,100
[Ward Area]

540
00:36:23,190 --> 00:36:24,570
Let's move faster.

541
00:36:25,320 --> 00:36:26,210
The patient from Dr. Zheng

542
00:36:26,210 --> 00:36:27,210
has to get on the plane quickly

543
00:36:27,320 --> 00:36:29,460
after it arrives.

544
00:36:30,320 --> 00:36:31,060
Patients inside the tent

545
00:36:31,190 --> 00:36:32,500
who need to be sent to Dr. Zheng

546
00:36:32,500 --> 00:36:33,340
for intervention

547
00:36:33,340 --> 00:36:34,420
should be prioritized.

548
00:36:34,990 --> 00:36:36,250
We must make a clear distinction.

549
00:36:36,250 --> 00:36:36,730
Yes.

550
00:36:37,360 --> 00:36:38,940
There are still beds available
in the front tent.

551
00:36:42,280 --> 00:36:42,940
Watch your step.

552
00:36:44,070 --> 00:36:45,020
Commander Zhao!

553
00:36:48,470 --> 00:36:49,130
Commander Zhao!

554
00:36:49,440 --> 00:36:50,340
How's it going over there?

555
00:36:50,720 --> 00:36:51,690
They've been treating them.

556
00:36:52,070 --> 00:36:53,250
Zheng is really good.

557
00:36:53,470 --> 00:36:54,770
He solved a big problem by intervening.

558
00:36:56,320 --> 00:36:57,730
Good. Thank you.

559
00:36:57,730 --> 00:36:58,290
OK.

560
00:36:58,880 --> 00:36:59,940
Did he really do an intervention

561
00:36:59,940 --> 00:37:01,170
with a gastrointestinal machine?

562
00:37:01,630 --> 00:37:02,650
How did he do it?

563
00:37:03,840 --> 00:37:04,730
Blind maneuver maybe.

564
00:37:05,840 --> 00:37:06,860
Let's work harder.

565
00:37:08,590 --> 00:37:09,690
Next patient.

566
00:37:09,700 --> 00:37:13,340
[Nanyang Town Health Center]

567
00:37:19,630 --> 00:37:20,380
Next patient.

568
00:37:20,510 --> 00:37:21,210
Zheng.

569
00:37:21,510 --> 00:37:22,590
It's been all night.

570
00:37:22,590 --> 00:37:23,380
It's dawn.

571
00:37:23,380 --> 00:37:24,210
Get some rest.

572
00:37:24,360 --> 00:37:24,980
Besides,

573
00:37:24,980 --> 00:37:25,690
the amount of radiation

574
00:37:25,840 --> 00:37:26,820
