575
00:37:27,110 --> 00:37:28,020
The sooner we can remove the clot,

576
00:37:28,070 --> 00:37:29,250
the better she'll recover.

577
00:37:29,590 --> 00:37:30,340
Next.

578
00:37:30,400 --> 00:37:31,380
Take a break.

579
00:37:31,800 --> 00:37:32,730
I'll clean the wound.

580
00:37:33,070 --> 00:37:33,980
Yes.

581
00:37:34,070 --> 00:37:35,020
Take a break.

